    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Oaths, verbal or written, usually mandatory, affirming the loyalty of the takers, such as to a government, ruler, constitution, or set of principles.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
